description.content:
I will develop a complete Wordpress eCommerce Multi Vendor Marketplace website for your Starter, Business or Enterprise. A perfect Multi Vendor e-commerce Solution.
What Multi Vendor Marketplace Website would include?
  1. Independent Stores with Insights with Reports and Statement
  2. Frontend Dashboard for Vendors and Customers
  3. Earn from Each Sale (Fixed/Percentage)
  4. Easy Withdraw System for Your Vendors in multi vendor website.
  5. Activate/Deactivate a Vendor Selling Rights & Products
Consultation:
I offer Free Consultation, so do not hesitate to get in touch with me regarding multi vendor ecommerce marketplace website or any business website.

reviews.comment: Very nice and professional guy. He helped me make a very complex multivendor website that fit my budget. I talked to a bunch of other website developers and Tanveer was the best. We set up multiple Zoom calls and he was able to listen to my requests the whole way and get my website to look and function exactly how I wanted it. He would respond very quickly with very helpful answers. He is clearly an expert at what he does and speaks great English. A very good communicator that knows how to deliver according to your needs. Will definitely be getting more work done by him in the future. If you’re trying to find the one to build your website, choose him. He is the best and you won’t regret it.
Working  with him was a nice experience  and he is very cooperative.
